title: MisterMusic Show 308 New indie,alternative,rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 308 [120 minutes] 192kbps MP3 stereo


On this week's show new music from The Rentals, Angus & Julia Stone, The Rosebuds, and another new tune from the latest album by 
Bob Mould.
Plus a big alternative rock tune from June 1992 is the 'Oldie of the Week'. A song that was number 1 on the US modern rock chart for 4 weeks that summer.

It's a mix of indie, alternative, and rock tunes spanning 5 decades, beaming across the globe weekly- it's The MisterMusic Show.


The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
